            <h2 id="why-matters">üåç Why Do Personality Traits Matter?</h2>
            <p>Personality traits help us:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Understand ourselves better</li>
              <li>Predict how we might behave in different situations</li>
              <li>
                Improve how we relate to others‚Äîat school, work, or in
                relationships
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Psychologists have studied personality for decades and found that
              most people can be described using five major traits. This idea is
              called the Big Five Personality Traits, or the OCEAN model.
            </p>
