              üî¨ Where Do These Traits Come From?
            </h2>
            <p>
              These traits are not random. According to psychologists like Lewis
              Goldberg and McCrae & Costa, they come from a mix of:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Genetics (traits you‚Äôre born with)</li>
              <li>Life experiences (how you‚Äôre raised, what happens to you)</li>
              <li>Culture (what your society teaches you to value)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              The Big Five model has been tested in over 36 countries and dozens
              of languages. It‚Äôs also been used in fields like mental health,
              education, workplace hiring, and even relationship counseling.
            </p>
          </article>
