            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>‚ÄúI see myself as someone who is outgoing.‚Äù</li>
              <li>‚ÄúI tend to be organized and follow a schedule.‚Äù</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              You don‚Äôt need to study psychology to understand your
              personality‚Äîjust answer honestly!
            </p>
